nodes.text: A Nazzar male served as an icecrawler driver on the planet Syned for the Arkadianate in the year 1032 BBY. He was transporting a crawlerful of refugees from Diligence, a starship, to the capital city of Calimondretta when the captain of the ship, Jarrow Rusher, led a mutiny to steal the vehicle in preparation for an siege of Calimondretta. During a scuffle, Rusher killed the Nazzar by breaking his neck. Meanwhile, the other Arkadianate crew were killed by members of Team Ripper, led by Zeller.
